6.4.1 Player Control Settings
Customizable player controls offer users a more equitable experience when they can adjust skip duration, fast forward and rewind speeds, and other player control interactions.

6.4.1-A
The user must have the option to set skip speed in the playback at: 5, 10, 15, 20, 25, and 30 seconds.

6.4.1-B
Users must be able to customize the speed of the fast forward and rewind options.
